- Optimized performance for NUI end.

- Reworked YT API Player in order to fix issue with memory leak.
- Reworked NUI callbacks and some events to prevent UI lags due to the data traffic.
- Reworked sound effect system.
- Reworked documentation.
- Reworked main menu screen (welcome screen).
- Reworked base animations for all route changes.

- Created **"/ooc"** command as requested. Now it's a built-in command that send message to everyone on the server (global OOC).
- Created functionality for status colors presets that you can set through `Config.UI.CustomHudColors` table (make sure to set `use = true,` to use them!).
- Created export `Music_Reload` in case someone will need it.
- Created export `IsInterfaceVisible` to gather whether interface is visible or not.
- Created slider for sound effect volume.

- Added comments and variables for each of the command for "anonymous" state. Now you can set whether message should send character name or just the id of the player.
- Added `GetTime_Hours` & `GetTime_Minutes` to gather custom time in-game.
- Added param `Config.UI.AllowUseCustomTime` to allow use of the functions `GetTime_Hours` & `GetTime_Minutes`.
- Added param `Config.Chat.VisibilityTimeout` to handle how long chat should be visible.
- Added `Workers.CinematicMode.PreventOpen` & `Workers.GameMenu.PreventOpen`.
- Added event that listens for UI visibility state changes `ZSX_UIV2:Interface:VisibilityChanged`.

- Fixed issue with focus state that could cause temporary lack of the cursor.
- Fixed issue with `Config.UI.DisableVoiceIndicator` param not disabling non 3d voice indicator.
- Fixed cosmetic issue with chat message headers while using black color.
- Fixed issue with `/get_config_preset` command returning lowercased interface names.
- Fixed issue with seatbelt sound being heard when destroying entity.
- Fixed issue with minimap radar state not being refreshed.
